Social media platforms like Instagram generate massive amounts of engagement data, but content creators and businesses often struggle to understand:

Why certain posts receive higher engagement while others perform poorly
Which content types (Reels, posts, carousels) drive maximum reach and interaction
How posting time and frequency impact audience engagement
The effectiveness of hashtags and captions in increasing visibility

This project aims to analyze Instagram data to:

Improve overall engagement and content performance
Identify high-performing content strategies
Optimize posting time and hashtag usage
Enable data-driven decision-making for social media growth
